{"tid":2206610,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"籃球場一開返，玩具撚搞到成地垃圾薯條水樽口罩","createTime":"2020-09-17T14:42:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T07:15:30.000Z","uid":7439,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dac5929400aba40dc475b7566469458d0fd2b608","tid":2206610,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T14:42:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/119041038_761714691277682_3260913598414197948_n.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=eI7hFmcwXa8AX9OC9cB&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=1188493bfbcbf8c440ad4621a1bf8b02&amp;oe=5F88FD89\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F119041038_761714691277682_3260913598414197948_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3DeI7hFmcwXa8AX9OC9cB%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3D1188493bfbcbf8c440ad4621a1bf8b02%26oe%3D5F88FD89&h=ac595bee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃文萱 Leticia Wong<br />\n9月13日 20:26  &middot; <br />\n【開放返籃球場嘅第一個weekend】<br />\n放寬返限聚令，第一城都開放籃球場，文萱都落去巡咗轉，但第一個weekend除咗成個場都LeBron 、￼curry、harden之外，仲滿地垃圾，有外賣紙袋、有薯條，有水樽，仲有用過嘅紙巾，<br />\n同！埋！用！過！嘅！口！罩！<br />\n唔單止唔衛生，增加傳染風險，要清潔工友咁樣執啲口罩都唔好啦，係嗎？唔該各位扔垃圾好似你地射三分波咁，瞄返去個垃圾筒啦☺️<br />\n另外，管理處回覆咗文萱，表示係27座對出嘅遊樂場會成個翻新，但現階段仲招緊標，短時間內都仲未可以開放返，會跟進睇下可唔可以加快個進度🙏🏻<br />\n知道大家餓波餓咗好耐，但都請大家要注意返公德心同保持衛生，有手尾執返晒帶嚟嘅垃圾扔落垃圾桶🙏🏻拜託大家🙇🏻&zwj;♀️ 文萱會再巡查👀<br />\n而籃球場塊地係之前新鋪好㗎，希望大家錫住打啦😘<br />\n#教練我想打波 #三分波<br />\n#我都仲未有得打羽毛球呀<br />\n#唔該你地乖乖地攞走啲垃圾走<br />\n#鼠患 #係唔係你地<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/119088351_761714764611008_1180175829941557703_n.jpg?_nc_cat=111&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=SJ6m9qpMuCIAX9uhafh&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=57dc890c103ee04171f911f6a2d6e375&amp;oe=5F895568\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F119088351_761714764611008_1180175829941557703_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D111%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3DSJ6m9qpMuCIAX9uhafh%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3D57dc890c103ee04171f911f6a2d6e375%26oe%3D5F895568&h=67a2df8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/119198626_761714747944343_2166303590539378117_n.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=Y1FfgbGFaXEAX9nvYdk&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=d79da94677c725c499b2448faf71edb8&amp;oe=5F881485\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F119198626_761714747944343_2166303590539378117_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3DY1FfgbGFaXEAX9nvYdk%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3Dd79da94677c725c499b2448faf71edb8%26oe%3D5F881485&h=f48a2de6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/119060915_761714701277681_1835144762335202188_n.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=hR18-n_PtVUAX8nZja0&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=471708fef326c71fe3b91a8a12050f44&amp;oe=5F884919\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F119060915_761714701277681_1835144762335202188_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3DhR18-n_PtVUAX8nZja0%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3D471708fef326c71fe3b91a8a12050f44%26oe%3D5F884919&h=aa606ccf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"24942e37b9e5ea5571b0885292069edd62e2bcd2","tid":2206610,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T14:42:59.000Z","msg":"Kathy Lai<br />\nJoyce WA 同意。17座果邊夜晚成日有人揸車嚟打波，仲要就咁泊係籃球場見到嘅位置。<br />\n<br />\nKelvin Leonard<br />\n<span class=\"red\">鎖車隊放假？定班友有特權？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\nSamuel Leung<br />\nKathy Lai 特登揸車黎打咁誇張<br />\n <br />\nKathy Lai<br />\n以前成日泊喺17座，試過打去投訴，見住佢係籃球場行去揸架車，轉個彎停係19座後面避車處，再打過。"},{"pid":"604b5cfa34c22191a4322c127538667a63a68082","tid":2206610,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T14:43:32.000Z","msg":"HO Ekk<br />\n仲要一邊打波，又一邊食煙，超黑人憎。所以封哂啲場等佢哋無波打係_ _ _🤬<br />\n <br />\nJessica Tong<br />\n今日下晝路過球場見到啲人多到不得了，打波嘅打波，唔係打波坐埋一邊喺櫈都密密麻麻，仲要係冇戴口罩，到而家夜晚黑見到成個球場都係垃圾！啲人咁冇公德心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nAnthony Lee<br />\n今日下晝嚇死，多人到....以為今日第一城打籃球聯賽。個個場都打緊比賽，重有人跟隊。&rsquo;攝&rsquo;下射波都吾得,慘..<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a18a67ef000fbae59cccf7f1531d8029065c5a5","tid":2206610,"uid":7439,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T14:44:34.000Z","msg":"做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬鞍山區議員葉榮叫房署拆咗個籃球框，啲玩具撚激撚到。。。。。。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fJnQwS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fJnQwS</a>"},{"pid":"1f80541744b30b1817449cf6c651fbb46fc92e9f","tid":2206610,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T14:45:58.000Z","msg":"黃展翹：我bulk撚過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>（獨媒特約報導）沙田區議員黃文萱早前曾印製工作報告<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，內容包括一張其曾出席香港民意研究所記者會的照片，並寫上「香港民意研究所記者會」字眼。<span class=\"red\">民政處稱只能寫作「記者會」，否則將不會作出津貼，最後更拒絕批出款項。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港民意研究所在今年1月10日曾舉行記者會，公布「民主社區」計劃的民意調查報告，即集中研究沙田第一城及東區太古城西選區居民的意見。香港民意研究所曾邀請當區議員出席記者會，黃文萱及後將記者會的照片，列入其工作報告內容，付印後欲向民政處申請津貼。<br />\n<br />\n民政處職員表明，如不將字眼修改為「記者會」，該份工作報告不會獲得資助。黃文萱指出，由於每月的營運開支包括辦公室租金、助理薪酬等約5萬元，該份宣傳品約為3,000元，最後只能被迫抽起該宣傳品：「疫情嚴重要嗰陣時，要自己用人工買口罩，如果仲綑綁埋宣傳品同租金嗰啲一齊申報，唔知審查到幾時先有得攞返。」</blockquote>"},{"pid":"11cd7b37b1ef15219df00c4d8fe4b7607e62f455","tid":2206610,"uid":303133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T14:46:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /